"""
        Test that a MACSignatureKeyInformation struct can be built from a
        dictionary.
        """
client = ProxyKmipClient()
result = client._build_mac_signature_key_information(None)
self.assertEqual(None, result)
result = client._build_mac_signature_key_information({'unique_identifier':
    '1', 'cryptographic_parameters': {'cryptographic_algorithm': enums.
    CryptographicAlgorithm.AES}})
self.assertIsInstance(result, obj.MACSignatureKeyInformation)
self.assertEqual('1', result.unique_identifier)
self.assertIsInstance(result.cryptographic_parameters, obj.
    CryptographicParameters)
self.assertEqual(enums.CryptographicAlgorithm.AES, result.
    cryptographic_parameters.cryptographic_algorithm)
